---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Impressum | Bethke &amp; Partner" noindex={true} activePage="">

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <a href="/" class="page-back">← Zurück zur Startseite</a>
    <span class="page-tag">Rechtliches</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">Impressum</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="legal-wrap">

  <div class="legal-section">
    <h2 class="legal-h2">Angaben gemäß § 5 TMG</h2>
    <div class="info-card">
      <div class="info-card-row">
        <span class="info-card-label">Unternehmen</span>
        <span class="info-card-value">Bethke &amp; Partner</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card-row">
        <span class="info-card-label">Adresse</span>
        <span class="info-card-value">Ostendstraße 111, 90482 Nürnberg</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card-row">
        <span class="info-card-label">Vertreten durch</span>
        <span class="info-card-value">Alexis Bethke-Pittadakis</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card-row">
        <span class="info-card-label">Telefon</span>
        <span class="info-card-value"><a href="tel:+4917675726791">0176 75726791</a></span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card-row">
        <span class="info-card-label">E-Mail</span>
        <span class="info-card-value"><a href="mailto:alexis@bethke-und-partner.de">alexis@bethke-und-partner.de</a></span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card-row">
        <span class="info-card-label">Steuernummer</span>
        <span class="info-card-value">240/204/71197</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card-row">
        <span class="info-card-label">Redaktionell verantwortlich</span>
        <span class="info-card-value">Alexis Bethke-Pittadakis</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section">
    <h2 class="legal-h2">EU-Streitschlichtung</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">Die Europäische Kommission stellt eine Plattform zur Online-Streitbeilegung (OS) bereit: <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr/</a>. Unsere E-Mail-Adresse finden Sie oben im Impressum.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section">
    <h2 class="legal-h2">Verbraucherstreitbeilegung</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">Wir sind nicht bereit oder verpflichtet, an Streitbeilegungsverfahren vor einer Verbraucherschlichtungsstelle teilzunehmen.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section">
    <h2 class="legal-h2">Bildnachweise</h2>
    <p class="legal-p">Teile des Bildmaterials auf dieser Website stammen von Unsplash.</p>
    <p class="legal-p">Foto Startseite: Redmind Studio auf Unsplash – „a group of people sitting around a wooden table"</p>
  </div>

</div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--navy); padding: 120px 40px 64px; }
  .page-hero-inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-back {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--slate-2); text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 32px; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .page-back:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .page-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue-mid); margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }
  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 54px); font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white); line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .legal-wrap { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 40px 100px; }
  .legal-section { margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .legal-section:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .legal-h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--navy);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-2);
  }
  .legal-h3 {
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--navy);
    margin: 24px 0 8px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .legal-p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .legal-p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .legal-p a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }
  .legal-p a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .info-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 32px 36px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .info-card-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
    gap: 4px 20px; padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 14px;
  }
  .info-card-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .info-card-label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; padding-top: 2px; }
  .info-card-value { color: var(--text); }
  .info-card-value a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero { padding: 100px 24px 48px; }
    .legal-wrap { padding: 40px 24px 72px; }
    .info-card { padding: 24px; }
    .info-card-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2px; }
  }
</style>
